            "text": "high-level, object-oriented programming language"
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " developed by Sun Microsystems (now owned by Oracle). Known for its portability, scalability, and stability, Java is used in everything from Android apps and web servers to enterprise software and financial systems."
